    <h4>Benifits :</h4>
    <p>Healthcare cover of Rs.5 lakh per family,The scheme provides those in need to get secondary healthcare benefits provided by specialists like cardiologists and urologists. Moreover, advanced medical treatment like that for cancer, cardiac surgery and other is also covered.Removing the burden of out-of-pocket expenses, PMJAY aims to make the entire process of paying for healthcare cashless.Improvement of quality of life of the population.</p>
    </div>
