    <h4>Application Procedure :</h4>
    <ul>
     <li>Visit pmjay.gov.in and click on ‘Am I Eligible’</li>
     <li>Enter your mobile number and the CAPTCHA code and click on ‘Generate OTP’</li>
     <li>Then select your state and search by name/ HHD number/ ration card number/ mobile number</li>
     <li>Based on the search results you can verify if your family is covered under PMJAY</li>

   </ul>  
    
